text: Münzenberg is a town in Wetteraukreis in Hesse, Germany. It is 13 km north of Friedberg and is 16 km southeast of Gießen. Münzenberg Castle is outside the town. == Districts == Münzenberg has 4 districts: * Gambach * Münzenberg * Ober-Hörgern * Trais == References == == Other websites == * Category:Wetteraukreis
